Aisling Bea is an Irish comedian, actress, and writer who has gained recognition for her comedic talent and versatile performances. Born Aisling Cliodhnadh O'Sullivan, she adopted the stage name Aisling Bea for her career. She has appeared in various comedy shows, including "8 Out of 10 Cats" and "Live at the Apollo," as well as acted in television series such as "The Fall" and "Living with Yourself." Aisling has also written and starred in her own comedy series called "This Way Up," showcasing her skills as a writer and actor.
